{"tid":2333410,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中共航空母艦山東號戰鬥群通過台灣海峽 台灣海空軍派遣6艦8機監控並警戒 國防部長及參謀總長坐鎮大直要塞指揮","createTime":"2020-12-20T11:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T11:38:44.000Z","uid":292499,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ae89ca599eb3014ab10a4dce04d12545f2680c","tid":2333410,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"國防部指出，期間國軍除運用聯合情監偵系統全程掌握、監控外，並派遣6艘海軍各型艦船、8架次空軍各型機進行警戒、監控，依規定適切應處。<br />\n<br />\n山東號航空母艦是大陸首艘自製航母於去年12月17日服役、命名，此行至少伴隨三艘護衛艦，計畫前往三亞港。山東號此行引發我軍高度關注，國防部長嚴德發、參謀總長黃曙光今日都在大直衡山指揮所監控此事，我軍艦艇全程尾隨山東艦群。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012205007.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202012205007.aspx&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=67e010c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012205007.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/5107681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F5107681&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=1aabc8cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/5107681</a>"},{"pid":"cae7f4b24432bb1a177f1bf6f539029aea6a52c5","tid":2333410,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573415755267bfceed4a1dcb742779915720b437","tid":2333410,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/d